{"tid":448980,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人玩過屎","createTime":"2017-10-26T17:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T10:26:51.000Z","uid":103380,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a151d42622fd9290f7d2ae2e2ff1a630b02d7613","tid":448980,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"細過4-5歲記得印象好深刻<br />\n痾左條好靚既警棍屎 <br />\n之後見到個屎塔咁乾淨既水又有條咁靚既屎<br />\n就想拎起黎研究舊屎<br />\n但係又唔知點解會識整污糟 <br />\n抆左個保鮮袋當手套就拿左條屎上黎<br />\n個手感又唔係好硬但係揸上手又唔會爛<br />\n聞落又唔係好臭 玩左一陣就掉左落垃圾桶<br />\n後尾老母見到就問 一問就知係我 <br />\n佢笑到依加都會拎出黎笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b82a9143d0e2b714a6f11692b3ec830767662d","tid":448980,"uid":90978,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:27:39.000Z","msg":"BB仔唔識坐屎塔，用痰罐去，有日去大，大完我拎咗個匙羹係度攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇到我姑媽大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ef7367295613b06ce14907a46d7ce926472d47","tid":448980,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:27:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"53f304551aef0fdcb754bb9d906cb45f252c94ed","tid":448980,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BB仔唔識坐屎塔，用痰罐去，有日去大，大完我拎咗個匙羹係度攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇到我姑媽大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痾撚線 有冇&rsquo;不&lsquo;黎食"},{"pid":"a5cd4475a86f6d1cbab1567b5eb90173a26132ab","tid":448980,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34594c8ea0ee5f51a526c1e0761820cc